title: Thai beauty queen to dress like a tuk-tuk at Miss Universe
text: > Entertainment Thai beauty queen to dress like a tuk-tuk at Miss Universe This illustration released Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, by Miss Universe Thailand Organizer shows Miss Universe Thailand 2015 Aniporn Chalermburanawong wearing a dress that looks like a â€œtuk-tuk," a three-wheeled motorized taxi. The "Tuk Tuk Thailand" dress will be worn by Aniporn in the costume round at the pageant in December in the United States. It was the winning design from 356 entries in a contest held by Miss Universe Thailand. (Miss Universe Thailand Organizer via AP)
